children.subject: You are right that HKN and COE offer free tutoring for EE16A. If those don't work for you, please contact Nicole McIntyre at nicolemcintyre@berkeley.edu. She currently has seven available EE 16A tutors.

history.content: I'm looking to hire a private tutor for help with EE16A. I'm aware that there are societies that do tutoring, but it can get really crazy sometimes with all the people that show up. Are there any websites or bulletin boards? Pay $25/hr (negotiable) via Venmo -- weekends preferred -- send qualifications to awal@berk. Thanks!
